PrecisAppointment of Glen Wright, of Waterloo, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Broadcasting Corporation to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, effective August 22, 1991, in the place of Brian G. Armstrong, whose term will expire.
